      <h2
        class="text-[2rem]/[2.4rem] sm:text-[3rem]/[3.4rem] md:text-[4rem]/[4.4rem] font-bold"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic"
        data-aos-delay="200"
      >
        <span
          class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-[#66AFFF] to-blue"
        >
          Stay motivated
        </span>
        by seeing how far you’ve grown.
      </h2>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
